  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 103, The French Test.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第103课——法语考试。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "How long did the exam last?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "考试持续了多长时间？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "How was the exam, Richard?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "考试怎么样，理查德？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Not too bad.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "不算太糟。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I think I passed in English and mathematics.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我想我的英语和数学及格了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "The questions were very easy.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那些题很容易。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "How about you, Gary?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你呢，加里？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "The English and Maths papers weren't easy enough for me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "英语和数学试卷对我来说不够容易。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "I hope I haven't failed.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我希望自己没有不及格。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "I think I failed the French paper.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我想我的法语考试没及格。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "I could answer sixteen of the questions.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我能回答其中16道题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "They were very easy, but I couldn't answer the rest.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那些题很容易，但其余的我答不出来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "They were too difficult for me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "它们对我来说太难了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "French tests are awful, aren't they?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "法语考试糟透了，不是吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "I hate them.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我讨厌法语考试。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "I'm sure I've got a low mark.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我肯定自己的分数很低。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "Oh, cheer up.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "哦，振作点。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "Perhaps we didn't do too badly.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "也许我们考得不算太差。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "The guy next to me wrote his name at the top of the paper.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "坐在我旁边的那个考生只在试卷顶端写了自己的名字。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "Then he sat there and looked at it for three hours.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "然后他坐在那里，对着试卷看了三个小时。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "text": "He didn't write a word.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "一个字也没写。"
      }
    }
  ],
